data.description: Incredible investment opportunity for long-term & short-term rentals like Airbnb. Charming Multi-Family property features 3 units on a 13,200SF treed lot. Each unit offers a cozy living experience, with Unit 1 & 2 at 1,000SF & Unit 3 at 910SF. Enjoy a soothing interior w/neutral colors, elegant ceramic tile flooring, & stylish 6-panel doors. Unit 1 features a floor-to-ceiling fireplace, inviting kitchen w/granite cnrtps, white cabinetry & full-height bcksplash, dining area, primary bdrm w/ walk-in closet, an additional bdrm, 1 full bath, & a fenced backyard. Ample parking available. Close to the airport & minutes from Seattle. Nearby parks, sports fields, trails, & a community center/gym provide abundant recreation options. Don't miss this!
